Rating: 4
My boyfriend who loves pork and barbeque raved about this dish. I also served it to friends who were equally impressed. The second time I made it, I did add 1/4 c. vinegar to the brine in order to tenderize the pork and this improved it. I also used raisins instead of dates and more garlic and onion. We loved the results. Great for company.

